        "created_at": "2019-01-03T03:55:06.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"148598\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Not sure if you had the 08 Les Fournaux or not, but this sounds like a step up from it, as I gave it an 88-89 only. Really couldn\u2019t get past the sharp acidity of the vintage.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>My check-in for vintage 2008 a couple days ago was a Raphet Chambolle-Musigny. Definitely showing that sharp acid edge, but I like it. Interesting to hear the acid made it down to the Beaune area too.</p>",
